{"tid":1348652,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Herman Yeung我屌你老母","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:47:04.000Z","uid":213463,"like":416,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d58590b5839600348d1fcac36ced72b58d7a122f","tid":1348652,"uid":213463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/95273677335/posts/10156524131547336?s=1712332369&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F95273677335%2Fposts%2F10156524131547336%3Fs%3D1712332369%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d1f9ff1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/95273677335/posts/10156524131547336?s=1712332369&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚咁大單嘢你出個咁嘅post姐係算點 各打50大板？<br />\n<br />\n反對以暴易暴真係難聽過粗口，大家有睇live有睇片都睇到個男人跪係架西鐵度都比黑社會一拳打低<br />\n<br />\n咁你都可以反對以暴易暴？你含撚啦 屌你老母 扮傻<br />\n<br />\n成個post d留言都係屌鳩你 你咁鍾意咪del曬佢地囉<br />\n<br />\n而家香港人都好忙 唔得閒搞你 件事完左再慢慢清算你"},{"pid":"e899919c5c46f15e221536691bb4006864f8716d","tid":1348652,"uid":217096,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"dont make stupid ppl famous"},{"pid":"7c6b7caf8e921bfc3778213b6cb4d26beab7c455","tid":1348652,"uid":146094,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"傻9唔撚駛理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0d26b243d9bfd0d20f8202acb4eb9472849a9b","tid":1348652,"uid":124584,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"條傻撚三姓家奴黎 喺補習界都臭晒朵 近年焗住扮清高搞網上補習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c3aa895b4d9ca06dde869ca47c50bfd0c308e0","tid":1348652,"uid":15660,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"揚曬清高"},{"pid":"62f9b1ea6e9df7aa47516adbeb88a3bca6712c03","tid":1348652,"uid":21501,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"cit